8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Elai and Vidnoz share a solid foundation of core features including Text To Video, Avatar Talking Head, Auto Captions, Templates. Where Elai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Stock Footage and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Elai holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Vidnoz scores 5/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Vidnoz comes in at a lower starting price of $14.99/mo, while Elai begins at $23/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Elai's free tier and Vidnoz's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
